# Keep React type packages out of pnpm's hidden hoist fallback
# (node_modules/.pnpm/node_modules). The workspace holds two React worlds —
# storefront/wholesale on @types/react@19, rewardspro (Polaris/Remix) on
# @types/react@18 — and the hoist winner is nondeterministic. Next.js's own
# .d.ts files resolve `react` through that fallback, so an 18.x winner breaks
# the React-19 apps' typecheck. Unhoisted, every app resolves @types/react
# from its own declared dependency. Types are compile-time only; nothing
# resolves them at runtime, so unhoisting is safe.
hoist-pattern[]=*
hoist-pattern[]=!@types/react
hoist-pattern[]=!@types/react-dom
